strings:
<voice_0x010013EA><se_high>*: (W-Who are those people!?
Their clothes are so colourful!
Are they friends of Empyrea?)
<voice_0x010013EB><se_def>*: (No, no! Look at them! Apart from their bright clothes, they're nothing like Empyrea.)

<voice_0x010013EC><se_def>*: (...I think they look like humans! Yes.
They look strange, but they're still humans!)
<voice_0x010013ED><se_high>*: (Humans!? But I thought Empyrea is the only one who can look so colourful...)

<voice_0x010013EE><se_def>*: (Now, now! Stay calm!
They're not dangerous, so don't get carried away.
Call the Chief!)
<voice_0x010013F0><se_low>Chief: Ah... So this is what all the fuss was about...
<voice_0x010013F1><se_low>Chief: If I'm not mistaken, you must have come through the Dark Eye. You are dwellers from the World of Light, no?
<voice_0x010013F2><se_low>Chief: Just as I thought. Then it must be the will of the Goddess that brings you to us.

<voice_0x010013F3><se_low>Chief: Well...
There is something I wish to discuss with you.
Perhaps you would visit me in my home later.

<voice_0x010013F4><se_low>Chief: If you'll just promise me that, you can take your time and look around the village as much as
you like.
<voice_0x010013F5><se_low>Chief: I will be waiting, then. My home is the largest dwelling here, so you'll know where to find me.
<voice_0x010013F6><se_low>Chief: Flock of Empycchu! Let us go back to our work and carry on as normal! Do not forget to be kind to strangers!

<voice_0x010013F7><se_low>Chief: Please! There is no need to hide it!
It is quite clear from your vivid appearance.

<voice_0x010013F8><se_low>Chief: Let me ask you again.
Are you dwellers from the World of Light?
